	‚Ä¢	high-abstraction reasoning
	‚Ä¢	multi-model integration
	‚Ä¢	generating entirely new doctrine

Vector memory retrieves data,
but cannot retrieve meaning or identity.

PantheonOS solves this limitation via symbolic scaffolding.

